casebody.data:
State of North Carolina
v.
Titus Batts No. 104P11-8 Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 8, 2016. Ms. Kimberly N. Callahan, Assistant Attorney General, Mr. Ernie Lee, District Attorney, For State of North Carolina. Mr. Titus Batts, Pro Per.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 11th of October 2016 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the North Carolina Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 8th of December 2016."
